<p>After completing his undergraduate studies in Financial Mathematics at Istanbul Bilgi University, he started to work as an Auditor in an international independent audit firm. He is still working as an advisor in an international company after his MBA education at Bahçeşehir University. He volunteered at the Community Volunteers Foundation during his university years, then he was a member of the board of directors and board of trustees. He is a member of the Supervisory Board of Sen De Gel since its inception. In addition, he has been a member of founding membership, board of directors and board of auditors in various non-governmental organizations working in different fields. He speaks English and German. He is married and has two children.</p>